<span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large">,</span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">&nbsp;iemūžināt </span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-tiny">(skatierakstā)</span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large">, [sarunvalodai] </span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">Ielentot</span></span></b></p><p><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Filózōfs </span><span class="moze-tiny" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">(filozofs)</span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"> ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Prātinieks</span><span style="color: #000000"> </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span class="moze-tiny">(</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/pr%C4%81tnieks:1" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">æsot&nbsp;novæcojusi nozīme</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">); nievājoši lietot vārdu „prātinieciņš” arīdz „prātinieķelis”)</span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">, prātonis</span><br><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Filózōfisks </span><span class="moze-tiny" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">(filozofisks)</span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> ---&gt; </span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #00a022">Prātiniecisks</span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">, prātonisks</span><br><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Filózōfija </span><span class="moze-tiny" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">(filozofija)</span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> ---&gt; </span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #00a022">Prātiniecība</span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">, prātonība</span></p><p><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Finansēt ---&gt; </span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #00a022">Apnaudot</span><br><span style="color: #000000">Finansēšana ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Apnaudošana</span><span style="color: #000000">, </span><span style="color: #00a022">apnaude</span><br><span style="color: #000000">Finansējums ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Apnaudojums</span><br><span style="color: #000000">Finanses ---&gt; [naudas apgrozījums] Naudaprite, naudrite / [naudas līdzekļu kopums] Naudājs, naudiens, naudekļi, naudeklājs</span><br><span style="color: #000000">Finansiāls ---&gt; Naudisks, naudeklisks | Naudas </span></span><span class="moze-tiny" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">(kas)</span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br>Finansists ---&gt; </span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #00a022">Naudlietis</span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">, naudlietinieks, naudvedis, naudzinis, naudinieks, naudeklinieks</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-large">Fints, māņu kustība, māņkustība ---&gt; Maldenis, mānenis, māņa,&nbsp;</span><span class="moze-large">viltkusts</span><span class="moze-large">, maldkusts, māņkusts<br>Fintot, veikt/izdarīt māņu kustību ---&gt; Maldeņot, māneņot, viltkustot, māņkustot<br>Fintotājs ---&gt; Maldeņotājs, māneņotājs, viltkustotājs, māņkustotājs</span></span></span></p><p><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000">Flóte </span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny">(flote)</span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"> ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Jūrenājs</span><span style="color: #000000">, jūreniens</span></span><br><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Karaflóte </span><span class="moze-tiny" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">(karaflote)</span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> ---&gt; </span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 160, 34);" class="moze-large">Karajūrenājs</span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">, </span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 160, 34);" class="moze-large">jūras</span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> (kara) </span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 160, 34);" class="moze-large">sp</span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #00a022">ǣki</span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span class="moze-tiny"><span class="moze-large"><span class="moze-large"> </span></span></span></span><span class="moze-tiny" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">(</span><span class="moze-tiny" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">jūras kara spēki</span><span class="moze-tiny" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">)[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/mwe:134164" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" style="font-weight: bold;"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">]</span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">, karajūreniens<br></span><b><span class="moze-large">Gaisa flóte</span></b> <span class="moze-tiny">(gaisa flote)</span> <b><span class="moze-large">---&gt; <span style="color: #00a022">Lideklājs</span>, laistuvājs, laidoklājs</span></b><br><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Flótila <span class="moze-tiny" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">(flotila)</span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> ---&gt; Jūreņvienība</span></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">Flōrbōls</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny"> (florbols) </span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">---&gt; </span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #00a022">Grīdbumbiņa</span></span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large"> </span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny">(lietuviski - „grindų riedulys” 'grīdas bumbiņa')</span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">, grīdasbumba<br></span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">Flōrbōlists</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny"> (florbolists)</span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large"> ---&gt; </span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #00a022">Grīdbumbiņinieks</span></span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">, grīdbumbiņonis, grīdasbumbinieks</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">Fluīds ---&gt; </span><span style="font-weight: bold;" class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">Plūsnis</span></span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">, plūstenis, plūstis, plūsts<br>Fluidāls ---&gt; </span><span style="font-weight: bold;" class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">Plūsnisks</span></span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">, plūstenisks<br>Fluidifikācija ---&gt; </span><span style="font-weight: bold;" class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">Šķidrināšana</span></span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-large">, plūsnināšana, plūstenināšana<br>Fluīdistōrs </span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-t