w">V-T</a>]</span></span><span class="moze-large"><br><span style="color: #000000">Jokoties ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #fff800">Smīdoties</span><span style="color: #000000">, smieties, smiet</span><br><span style="color: #000000">Jocīgs, jokains ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Smieklīgs</span><span style="color: #000000">, smīdinošs / [dīvains, savāds] </span><span style="color: #00a022">Smieklīgs</span><span style="color: #000000"> </span></span><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/p%C5%ABkains" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]</span></span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #000000">, pūkains </span></span><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/p%C5%ABkains" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">SARVV-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]</span></span></b></p><p><b style=""><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large">Jurists ---&gt; </span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">Tiesībinieks</span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large"> </span><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/ties%C4%ABbnieks" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]</span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large">, tiesībzinātninieks </span><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/ties%C4%ABbzin%C4%81tnieks" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny"> „tiesībzinātnieks”]</span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large">, tiesībzinātniķis, likuminieks </span><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/likumnieks" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">NOVCV-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]</span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large"><br>Jurisprudence ---&gt; </span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">Tiesībzinātne</span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large"> </span><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/ties%C4%ABbzin%C4%81tne" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]</span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large">, tiesībiniecība<br>Juridisks ---&gt; </span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">Tiesisks</span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large"> </span><span style="color: #000000" class=""><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/juridisks" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]</span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-large"><br>Juridizācija ---&gt; </span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">Tiesiskošana</span><br><span style="color: #000000">Jurisdikcija ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Tiesasvara</span></span></b></p>
                        <h1 style="text-align: left;"><b><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #000000">K</span></span></b></h1><p><b><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #000000">Kalendārs ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Dienlapis</span><span style="color: #000000">, </span><span style="color: #000000">dienrādis</span><span style="color: #000000"> </span></span><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/dienr%C4%81dis" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]</span></span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #000000">, dienenis<br>Kalendārs </span></span><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-tiny">(saistīts ar kalendāru)</span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #000000"> ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Dienlapisks</span><span style="color: #000000">, </span><span style="color: #000000">dienrādisks</span><span style="color: #000000">, dienenisks</span></span></b></p><p><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000">Kalpot </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-tiny">(kādam)</span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"> ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Klausīt</span><span style="color: #000000"> </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-tiny">(kādam)</span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"><b><span class="moze-large" style="text-align: start; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style="text-align: start; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal"><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/klaus%C4%ABt" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]</span></span></b></span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"><b><span style="text-align: start; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal" class="moze-large">, klausīt </span><span style="text-align: start; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal" class="moze-tiny">(kādu)</span><span style="text-align: start; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal" class="moze-large">, aiz</span></b><span class="moze-large">klausīt</span></span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"> </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-tiny">('klausīt kāda labad', priedēkļa nozīme kā vārdam „aizdars“ ir „aizdarīt”)</span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/aizklaus%C4%ABt" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">APVV-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]</span></span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000">, klausmot&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" class="moze-tiny">(no vārda „klausme” 'klausīšana'; aizvietojums vārdam „dienēt” ir „kalpošana”)</span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000">, klausmēt, klausiniekot, būt (kāda) klausiniekam / [par rīku] </span><span style="color: #00a022">Klausīt</span><span style="color: #000000">, derēt, lietoties</span><br><span style="color: #000000">Izkalpot ---&gt; Izklausīt, izklausmot, izklausmēt</span><br><span style="color: #000000">Izkalpoties ---&gt; Izklausīt, izklausmoties, izklausmēties / Izpelnīties </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/izpeln%C4%ABties" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]</span></span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"><br>Nokalpot ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Noklausīt</span><span style="color: #000000">, izklausīt </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/izklaus%C4%ABt" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">APVV-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]</span></span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000">, noklausmot, noklausmēt<br>Kalpošana ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Klausīšana</span><span style="color: #000000">, klausme, aizklausīšana, aizklausme<br>Pakalpot ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Paklausīt</span><span style="color: #000000">, patecēt</span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000">&nbsp;/ Palīdzēt<br></span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><b style=""><span class="moze-large" style="text-align: start; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal;"><span style="color: #000000">Pakalpojums ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Paklausījums</span><span style="color: #000000">, patecējums </span></span></b><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="text-align: start; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal"><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/patec%C4%93jums" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">] </span><span class="moze-large">/ Palīdzība, palīdziens, palīdzējums</span></span></b></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"><br>Apkalpot ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Apklausīt</span><span style="color: #000000">, apdarīt, aptecēt </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/aptec%C4%93t:2" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]</span></span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000">, aprūpēt </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/apr%C5%ABp%C4%93t" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]</span></span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"> / [Vadīt arba/gan uzturēt kārtībā (ierīci, iekārtu)] </span><span style="color: #00a022">Aprūpēt</span><span style="color: #000000"> </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-tiny">(ko)</span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000">, gādāt </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"><span class="moze-tiny">(par ko)[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/g%C4%81d%C4%81t:1" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny">]</span></span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000">, apdirbt, apdarbot<br></span></span><span class="moze-large" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">Apkalpotājs,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: start; font-style: normal;"><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;">óficiants </span><span class="moze-tiny">(oficiants)</span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"> ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Viesklausis</span><span style="color: #000000">, </span><span style="color: #00a022">viesmīlis</span><span style="color: #000000"> </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-tiny">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/viesm%C4%ABlis" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-tiny">] </span><span class="moze-large" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">/ [tāds, kas tīra t</span><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="text-align: start; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal" class="moze-large">æ</span></b><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #000000">lpas arīdz kādu vietu] </span><span style="color: #00a022">Apkopinieks</span><span style="color: #000000">, apkopējs&nbsp;</span></span><span class="moze-tiny" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">[</span><a href="https://tezaurs.lv/apkop%C4%93js" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><span class="moze-tiny">V-T</span></a><span class="moze-tiny" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">]</span><br></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000">Apkalpe ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Apkope</span><span style="color: #000000"> | [tie, kas to veic] </span><span style="color: #00a022">Apkopēji</span><span style="color: #000000">, apkopņi / [karinieku kopa, kas dirbj ar ir ap ieroci] </span><span style="color: #00a022">Aprūpji</span><span style="color: #000000">, <b><span style="text-align: start; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal">aprūpe,&nbsp;</span></b>aprūpņi, aprūpinieki / </span><span style="color: #00a022">Apklausme</span><span style="color: #000000">, </span><span style="color: #00a022">apklausīšana</span><span style="color: #000000">, apklause<br>Pašapkalpošanās kase ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Bezpārdevēja maksātne</span><br><span style="color: #000000">Kalpināt ---&gt; </span><span style="color: #00a022">Verdzināt</span><span style="color: #000000">,&nbsp;</span><span class="moze-large"><span style="color: #00a022">klausināt</span><span style="color: #000000">,&nbsp;</span></span><span style="color: #000000">dirbināt </span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000" class="moze-tiny">('likt dirbt')</span></span><span class="moze-large" style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="color: #000000"> / Pielietot<br><span style="